   <title id="title__Toc50994870">CLEANSCREENSTATE System Variable</title>
   <conbody>
      <section><title>Clean screen state</title><p>Specifies whether clean screen state is active or not. Clean screen state is controlled by the CLEANSCREENON and CLEANSCREENOFF commands. Activating the clean screen state makes the drawing area larger by hiding elements of the user interface.</p>
